metadata.name: Human
metadata.description: A human is an individual who is interested in to be a member of the NFT space but may not have any prior experience or expertise in the field. They are eager to learn and explore the various options available to them, and are open to the possibility of becoming any of these options including Creator, Curator, Marketer, Advisor, Educator or Art collector. They are willing to put in the effort to develop their skills and knowledge, and are motivated to succeed in the NFT industry. But unfortunately, not all of them gonna succeed..
